{"tid":803482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"翠河真喺好垃圾！","createTime":"2018-09-02T10:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T10:46:16.000Z","uid":204260,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4cafc7e480597953ea44d9d958721dc174f97eea","tid":803482,"uid":204260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T10:03:08.000Z","msg":"啲阿叔侍應自己聽唔清楚就大大聲吆喝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱講完飲凍奶茶<br />\n條廢老聽唔到就大大聲問你<br />\n&ldquo;飲乜嘢吖！&rdquo;<br />\n態度真喺好撚衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地一大班人<br />\n每一個都聽唔到同咁撚衰態度<br />\n&ldquo;你叫乜嘢吖！？&rdquo;<br />\n之後叫完又話無呢樣無嗰樣<br />\n嬲撚到唔撚食取消又屌鳩我做咩取消<br />\n大佬我想食嗰樣你又冇<br />\n我咪唔食囉<br />\n今日去送殯先唔屌返你<br />\n以後唔撚去幫襯<br />\n<br />\n利申:某殯儀館隔離街既翠河 打手死全家"},{"pid":"224fd71b720288f8cb4e6a0ef91ff873f69fe23a","tid":803482,"uid":204260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T10:11:44.000Z","msg":"真人真事<br />\n啱啱發生<br />\n仲<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/180942_6e6e8769fd7786c277689ef89a10aae6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F180942_6e6e8769fd7786c277689ef89a10aae6.png&h=cbf347de&s={SIZE}\" />食緊"},{"pid":"3402af9f183ec2eae9d5a299215657717cc71a1c","tid":803482,"uid":4826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T10:34:13.000Z","msg":"你最後咪又係食左"},{"pid":"b94b2ec4019cfcee49b0036e20f971617476affb","tid":803482,"uid":196719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T10:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575fea32f9b11e23b0fd57819d2a046b042facfb","tid":803482,"uid":185696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T10:42:08.000Z","msg":"隔離post$28一舊超大豬排<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/